{"tid":2062481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲籍男子涉販毒　被廣州法院一審判死刑","createTime":"2020-06-13T07:12:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T06:31:59.000Z","uid":82938,"like":123,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"3affc4f7b015fba913ce23c9de8c866f47bcaf2b","tid":2062481,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T07:12:06.000Z","msg":"內地傳媒報道，一名澳洲籍男子被指販毒，星期三被廣州市中級人民法院一審判決，以走私毒品罪判處死刑，沒收個人全部財產。外界關注事件會否令本身已經十分緊張的中澳關係進一步惡化。法院的通告未有交代案情。報道指，男子2013年12月在白雲機場被捕，在行李搜出7.5公斤冰毒澳洲政府早前呼籲國際社會，就新型冠狀病毒疫情來源，展開獨立調查後，與北京的雙邊關係就陷入僵局。中國近日就發布「安全提醒」，要求民眾勿前往澳洲旅遊及留學。<br />\n<br />\n2020-06-13 14:59:46<br />\n<br />\nrthk tg<br />\n<br />\n亮劍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac91b5670af409085a1e175b9df4df0bfe0ce5e1","tid":2062481,"uid":201604,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T07:12:56.000Z","msg":"想去澳洲販毒了"},{"pid":"1bf261affbaf329402a9e20c9e676e992c484a0c","tid":2062481,"uid":85586,"like":49,"dislike":1,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T07:13:14.000Z","msg":"嚟香港識隻popo咪無事囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b81937c391548638861c2c288e12aa568ab7f5","tid":2062481,"uid":228995,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T09:40:39.000Z","msg":"2013年，坐到今日"},{"pid":"faa005a0bf0a638d4c0230f1dcd0e748214a29da","tid":2062481,"uid":120678,"like":57,"dislike":3,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T09:43:14.000Z","msg":"擺明砌生豬肉<br />\n我就一世都唔會入境支那臭西國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed68eb73b82c16a21529f5bb859f5a91bfadd984","tid":2062481,"uid":8410,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T09:44:14.000Z","msg":"罪名係澳洲人"},{"pid":"31d03a2bcb3e4f409ee5196f804bd5d2014e13a2","tid":2062481,"uid":72020,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"quo